# {{ .projectName }}

Prometheus and Grafana monitoring stack.

## Quick Start

    cp .env.example .env
    docker compose up -d

## Access

* Prometheus: http://localhost:{{ .prometheusPort }}
* Grafana: http://localhost:{{ .grafanaPort }}

Add the Prometheus datasource in Grafana using the URL http://prometheus:9090.
Edit prometheus.yml to add your scrape targets and reload Prometheus with a POST to /-/reload.
